Class NetworkSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.stage.Window
      • javafx.stage.Stage
        • view.NetworkSetup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class NetworkSetup
extends javafx.stage.Stage
    This class sets up the GUI for the menu option "Networked Game". This class also contains the methods to handle scenarios in which the "OK" and "Cancel" buttons are pressed.
    Author:
    Trevor Freudig, Scott LaFerriere
